---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout-en.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Paid Social – Adorable | Meta Ads, LinkedIn, TikTok, YouTube"
	description="Data-driven paid social that actually works. Campaign strategy, optimization, tracking and reporting for Meta, LinkedIn, TikTok, YouTube and Pinterest."
	swedishPath="/paid-social"
>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="hero-title">Paid social that actually works.</h1>
				<p class="hero-intro">
					Data-driven marketing focused on what can be measured and improved. Adorable works with the entire chain – from strategy to daily optimization.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
				
				<div class="service">
					<h3>Campaign strategy</h3>
					<p>Audience analysis, channel thinking and budget allocation. Creative direction that balances brand and conversion. No generic templates – strategy that actually fits your business.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service">
					<h3>Activation and optimization</h3>
					<p>Setup and ongoing management of campaigns on Meta (Facebook/Instagram), LinkedIn, TikTok, YouTube and Pinterest. A/B testing, bid strategies and continuous adjustment based on data. For both B2B and B2C.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service">
					<h3>Tracking and measurement</h3>
					<p>Implementation of conversion tracking, attribution and reporting structures. So you know what actually works – not just what looks good in the dashboard.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service">
					<h3>Audit and analysis</h3>
					<p>Review of existing accounts with concrete recommendations. Identify waste, missed opportunities and problems that can be fixed. No 50-page reports – just what matters.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service">
					<h3>Reporting</h3>
					<p>Clear reports showing results, insights and next steps. Focus on what drives the business forward, not vanity metrics.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section section-contact">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
				<div class="contact-info">
					<p class="contact-name">Peter Rosdahl</p>
					<p><a href="mailto:peter@adorable.se" class="contact-link">peter@adorable.se</a></p>
					<p><a href="tel:+46708235787" class="contact-link">+46 70 823 57 87</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		background: #fff;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #000;
	}

	.hero-intro {
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #000;
	}

	.section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 3rem;
		color: #000;
	}

	.service {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.service:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.service h3 {
		font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: #000;
	}

	.service p {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #333;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.section-contact {
		background: #000;
		color: #fff;
		border-top: none;
	}

	.section-contact .section-title {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.contact-info {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.contact-name {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-link {
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.contact-link:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
		}

		.section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
